name: Tokemons #0018
description:
Tokemons is a crypto-collectibles project on Hicetnunc, taking the original 151 Pokemon and smashing them together at high speed to create Tokemons!

With a maximum supply of 3000, each Tokemon is unique and 1/1.

Tokemons are created in part using the tool Pokemonfusion
(Created by Alex Onsager - pokemon.alexonsager.net)
